content.427: Tulip Bulb/10/-300/Seeds -74/Tulip Bulb/Plant in spring. Takes 6 days to produce a colorful flower. Assorted colors.
content.429: Jazz Seeds/15/-300/Seeds -74/Jazz Seeds/Plant in spring. Takes 7 days to produce a blue puffball flower.
content.433: Coffee Bean/15/-300/Seeds -74/Coffee Bean/Plant in spring or summer to grow a coffee plant. Place five beans in a keg to make coffee.
content.472: Parsnip Seeds/10/-300/Seeds -74/Parsnip Seeds/Plant these in the spring. Takes 4 days to mature.
content.473: Bean Starter/30/-300/Seeds -74/Bean Starter/Plant these in the spring. Takes 10 days to mature, but keeps producing after that. Yields multiple beans per harvest. Grows on a trellis.
content.474: Cauliflower Seeds/40/-300/Seeds -74/Cauliflower Seeds/Plant these in the spring. Takes 12 days to produce a large cauliflower.
content.475: Potato Seeds/25/-300/Seeds -74/Potato Seeds/Plant these in the spring. Takes 6 days to mature, and has a chance of yielding multiple potatoes at harvest.
content.476: Garlic Seeds/20/-300/Seeds -74/Garlic Seeds/Plant these in the spring. Takes 4 days to mature.
content.477: Kale Seeds/35/-300/Seeds -74/Kale Seeds/Plant these in the spring. Takes 6 days to mature. Harvest with the scythe.
content.478: Rhubarb Seeds/50/-300/Seeds -74/Rhubarb Seeds/Plant these in the spring. Takes 13 days to mature.
content.745: Strawberry Seeds/0/-300/Seeds -74/Strawberry Seeds/Plant these in spring. Takes 8 days to mature, and keeps producing strawberries after that.
